WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:01.766
If you want to know something, ask me

2
00:00:01.766 --> 00:00:03.666
Talking behind my back, how can I answer you?

3
00:00:05.066 --> 00:00:06.133
You're really disobedient

4
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:07.633
How many times have I told you

5
00:00:07.633 --> 00:00:08.633
not to come looking for me?

6
00:00:09.566 --> 00:00:10.133
Wife

7
00:00:10.733 --> 00:00:12.100
you're just a wretch

8
00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:13.300
daring to drug my mother

9
00:00:16.033 --> 00:00:17.866
you're worse than an animal

10
00:00:17.966 --> 00:00:19.400
Yes, extremely vicious

11
00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:20.066
Jiang Yu Yong

12
00:00:20.066 --> 00:00:22.333
I've rejected you time and time again

13
00:00:22.333 --> 00:00:23.800
Don't take an inch and want a mile

14
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:26.200
I'm not pursuing this for now

15
00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:27.366
Let me tell you,

16
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:30.100
I will only love one person in this life

17
00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:31.466
Now get out

18
00:00:31.966 --> 00:00:32.933
Get out now

19
00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:35.866
Jian Dao, you'll pay for this

20
00:00:41.133 --> 00:00:41.666
Wife

21
00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:44.033
how did the talk with President Li go?

22
00:00:44.433 --> 00:00:45.200
All good

23
00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:49.000
Today at the signing ceremony

24
00:00:49.666 --> 00:00:51.566
because of my mother, I lost my temper

25
00:00:53.833 --> 00:00:55.933
You've been with Jiang Yu Yong all along, haven't you?

26
00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:57.833
How could that be, wife?

27
00:00:57.833 --> 00:00:59.300
You still want to deceive me?

28
00:01:00.866 --> 00:01:01.833
Wife, I'm sorry

29
00:01:02.733 --> 00:01:05.366
My mistake was being too busy with work

30
00:01:05.366 --> 00:01:07.100
and neglecting your feelings

31
00:01:07.433 --> 00:01:08.600
But I think, wife

32
00:01:09.100 --> 00:01:10.800
you can't judge me like this

33
00:01:11.433 --> 00:01:12.333
Wife, look

34
00:01:12.333 --> 00:01:13.233
you're so fat now

35
00:01:13.233 --> 00:01:14.300
I've never despised you

36
00:01:14.300 --> 00:01:15.600
I've never left you

37
00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:17.266
so how could I do so now?

38
00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:19.533
I love you, wife

39
00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:22.466
Give me another chance

40
00:01:23.633 --> 00:01:24.533
No

41
00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:27.166
I have to stabilize Zhang Wen Xu first

42
00:01:28.533 --> 00:01:30.033
I'll give you one last chance

43
00:01:30.533 --> 00:01:31.433
Wife, I love you

44
00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:34.766
Today isn't convenient

45
00:01:37.066 --> 00:01:38.766
In my past life, I was too soft-hearted

46
00:01:38.766 --> 00:01:40.633
and believed your sweet lies

47
00:01:40.966 --> 00:01:43.233
So I ended up with such a tragic fate

48
00:01:43.566 --> 00:01:44.666
This time

49
00:01:45.066 --> 00:01:46.933
I won't be fooled again